 28th . Sunday May Letter write in paddock most of day with Ern Robo . Church servic in barn after tea . 100 men from Coy . on engin fatigu till 2am . 29th . Monday Fritz shell us out of our billet about 10am wreck hous much but our portion onli got one or two shell . Veri busi rescu gear munit from same between shot . Midday we took up our quarter in A.Coy . Redoubt few 100 yds along the road . Parti sent to clean up billet after shell also usual bath parad . At dusk 100 went on fatigu to trench , remaind back to billet where we slept . O.K. though expect more shell
